= image_tag "lottery.jpg"

%h1 Lunch Lottery

%p <b>#{@people_count} people</b> are going to lunch with a random group <b>every Tuesday.</b>

%p Sign up below! We'll email your group of 4 on Monday night.

- unless @person.errors.empty?
  .errors
    = @person.errors.full_messages

= form_for @person do |f|
  = f.label :email, "Email:"
  = f.text_field :email

  = f.submit "Sign me up!"